[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ヘルトさん、ゼロさんが決めた期限は１週間。\nそれまでにクリセルダさんたちを、「管理」……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00497",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そんなの、到底受け入れられないわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00498",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あのヘルトは気分屋なんでしょ？　性格をくすぐって、\nなんとかいい方向に持っていけないかしら？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00499",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "下手すると、要求がもっと過激になる危険もあるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00500",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "……何度言わせるのさ。あの二人と話し合うなんて\nどだい無理なんだ。異常気象、いや天災なんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00501",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "交渉しようなんて言った瞬間、逆らったと\n見なされるかもしれない。そうなったらどうなるか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00502",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あんたがこんな弱気になってるなんて\n初めてかも……よっぽど怖いのね、あの二人",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00503",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "でも、いくら強くても、残された時間が短くても\nあの人たちの言いなりになるわけにはいきません！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00504",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "まずは話し合いです。ですが……\nいざという場合も覚悟して、備えておきましょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00505",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "うん、そうだね！　アタシにできることがあったら\nなんでも言ってね！　手伝うよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00506",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "それなら、とりあえず回復薬でも\n準備しておいてもらいたいな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00507",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ジェロンさん！\nおケガ、大丈夫なんですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00508",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "このくらいは平気だ。またすぐに戦える",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00509",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "兄さんじゃなかったら全治数か月だと思いますよ。\nでも、兄さんはまだ戦うつもりで……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00510",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "当たり前だ。あのヘルトとかいう奴、\n長男の風上にも置けないからな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00511",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "カット",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "何が兄弟想いだ、本当にそうならば\nイェルカやヴァレリアに攻撃しないだろう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00512",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "カット",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "はは、そりゃあそうだ。アタシらは\n普通の兄弟から大きく外れちまってるんだねえ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00513",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "でも、それでも……やっぱり兄弟同士で\n争うなんて……そんなの嫌だよ。話し合えないかな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00514",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "ティムは優しいな……なあイェルカ。\nお前たち本当に話し合う余地はないのか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00515",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "アタシたちはあるけどね。\nただ、向こうがそうとは限らないってのが問題さ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00516",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "でも、ジェロンの言うことも分かるわ。\n少しでも可能性があるなら、諦めずに考えましょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00517",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ヴァレリア。粋なことを言うねぇ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00518",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00519",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]